modName: UNP BLESSED BODY- UNPB REDUX PROJECT
summary: The UNP Blessed Body increases the maximum size of the breasts for the UNP Body. Fully fix whether it is gap between meshes (hands-neck-body) or some weight paint error that cause deformation from its "predecessor" weighting process. Fully compatible with any UNP texture-hands-feet meshes. Animations for BBP included.
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=red][b]No need to tell you all why I upload this, it's my way to part with older pages. New page, New goodies with all good traits from previous. At the moment, I haven't add all "UNPB-related" mod to recommended. Soon I'll scan all of them and add them one by one.[/b][/color][b]

Hope can see your support and click

[youtube]k1bHxhBxEAc[/youtube] [youtube]sQ8bNUBcK2Q[/youtube][/b][/center][b]
[line]
[img]http://i232.photobucket.com/albums/ee187/Raestloz/Description.jpg[/img]
The UNP Blessed Body increases the maximum size of the breasts for the UNP Body. The end result is comparable to CBBE in cup-size while still maintaining the details we UNPers love. Nothing is changed but the breast size, and the shape is still in line with the latest UNP breasts (B2), just increased. From "Mosquito bites" to "Happy cushion". Don't worry, there's no "watermelon" .There also "lady lumps" version, LOL

Fully compatible with any UNP texture-hands-feet meshes.
Add New type of Body for "Push up" effect to make cleavage between the two. Inside the installer, it called "cleavage Project" and it only available on SFW version.
Fix gap between meshes (hands-neck-body) or some weight paint error that cause deformation from its "predecessor" weighting process.[/color]



[line]
[img]http://i232.photobucket.com/albums/ee187/Raestloz/installation.jpg[/img]
- Run package with Nexus Mod Manager and it will bring installation form for make your setup and prefenrences.
- [color=yellow]Optional - fore now has make integrated patch for CHSBHC-BBP arm fix which also will patch UNPB-BBP. You can download [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/11811]FNIS 3.x.x -Always necessary files[/url]. Recommended to use it.[/color]
[line]
[img]http://i232.photobucket.com/albums/ee187/Raestloz/know.png[/img]
This mod package has my latest configuration for XPMS (v1.9) and also options to choose
1. Nude or Nevernude
2. Support BBP or not
3. with or without animations also options type between (if you choose to install the animations)
- vanilla style or my VHH animations.
- Ordinary BBP (xp32) or Natural BBP (by darkangel).
- All directions (360) or default
4. Install the texture or not (your choice)
5. Use better hand meshes by Mr.Troublemaker
Since this mod using XPMS, you might need Realist Ragdoll & Force mod if you a player that like to drag corpses.

any issues related to texture problem is outside my(xp32) area. CBBE texture won't fit with this. Also texture seam will occur if you place incompatible set between face-body-hands-feet.

[img]http://i232.photobucket.com/albums/ee187/Raestloz/QA.jpg[/img]

[color=yellow]"Help! My huskarls aren't jiggling!"[/color]
Install [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4888]CHSBHC[/url] then install UNP then install UNPB-BBP, Lydia, Jordis and Iona will jiggle. Or just install the animations from CHSBHC. ORRR...install huskarls have feminine animations mod. ([color=red]thanks to mrtroublemaker for this fix[/color]) or [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/35155/]Correct Gender Animations by thefinn[/url], Use before you become Thane

[color=yellow]"Halp! My Orc Female isn't jiggling!"[/color]
There are a couple mods that change Orc race Females to use female animations. Try [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25495]
Orc female idle FIX[/url] or [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/16392]Feminine Female Orcs[/url] or [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/35155/]Correct Gender Animations by thefinn[/url]

[color=yellow]"Halp! My High and Wood Elf Female clothing/armour CTD!"[/color]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33470/]High and Wood elf skeleton fix by drywater509[/url]

[color=yellow]"Will this add muscles like in the picture?"[/color]
No. Muscles come from mods like [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13377]this one[/url]. The UNPB Body simply increases the breast size of the standard UNP body.

[color=yellow]"I have a custom texture/normal installed, will this affect that?"[/color]
Nope

[color=yellow]"Does this work with skinny UNP?" [/color]
no

[color=yellow]"Will this clip with my UNP armors?"[/color]
No. Armor meshes contain their own body mesh so using this as your base won't affect anything you wear.

[color=yellow]"Are there any armors for this?" [/color]
Yes and they are in the optional files section of this mod. xp32 is working on more ports, and I'm building some new armors specifically for this body.

[color=yellow]"I installed BBP version but when I wear ____ armor my boobs don't bounce!"[/color]
An armor has to be weighted and include the skeleton for BBP, which requires importing it to a 3d program and making it compatible. So only armors with BBP in the title will bounce.

[color=yellow]"I have some free time, interest, and want to help out. Where do I start?"[/color]
I will provide full support, and answer any questions, for anyone willing to take the plunge of converting/creating armors. I know blender, and nifskope. I learned from the [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3790]blender import-export tutorial[/url] on the nexus and the [url=http://wiki.tesnexus.com/index.php/Creating_an_armour_for_Skyrim._Part_1]custom armor tutorial on the nexus wiki[/url] and from asking questions of giants like dimon and caliente. And google.

[color=yellow]"Can you make a CBBE version?"[/color]
What?

[color=yellow]"I disagree with this mod."[/color]
No one is forced to dl. Dimon's awesome original version remains untouched on his mod page.
